name: Omiki
cleanBio: OMIKI is the Progressive Trance Project By Omri Amar From from Israel, has been producing electronic music since his early teens (16). Signed to the huge booking agency “ALTEZA Records" next to the top artists in the progressive trance scene. Touring around the globe for the last couple of years in huge Festivals and underground indoor parties. OMIKI did collaboration with leading artists like : Vini Vici, Timmy Trumpet, Neelix & Many More.  Omiki had some hits like : Balkan, Na Le, Devil In Me, Psycho, & many more that support by the top of the djs in the world.
